      "Let's talk.",
      "What should we chat about?",
      "Happy to help. What's up?",
      "Waiting for your input...",
      "What piques your interest?",
      "Prompt me.",
      "Here to help. What do you need?",
      "Tell me what you need.",
      "At your service.",
      "Awaiting instructions.",
      "What's on the agenda?",
      "What's the question?",
      "I'm listening.",
      "Ben's portfolio, your questions.",
      "Ready to assist.",
      "Ask something interesting.",
